==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Exmoor
<hw>Ex"moor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<etsep>Exmoor</etsep>, a district in Somersetshire and
Devonshire.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One of a breed of horned sheep of
Devonshire, England, having white legs and face and black nostrils. They
are esp. valuable for mutton.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A breed of ponies native to the Exmoor
district.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Exo-</ent>⟦br⟧
